@startuml
title ETR Study API — C4 Level 1 (system context)

top to bottom direction

actor "Integrator\n(HTTP client)" as Integrator
note right of Integrator
  **Out of scope:** web, mobile, bots.
  Any OpenAPI-compliant HTTP client.
end note

rectangle "ETR Study API\nFastAPI · OpenAPI · /api/v1" as Api

database "Relational store\n(SQLite dev · Postgres-capable)" as Db

rectangle "OCI image\nstudy-app-api" as Img

package "Observability\n(optional · Compose)" as Obs {
  [Grafana] as Graf
  [Prometheus] as Prom
  [Blackbox] as Bbx
}

package "Log search\n(optional)" as LogSearch {
  [Elasticsearch] as ES
  [Kibana] as Kib
}

Integrator --> Api : HTTPS · JSON
Api --> Db : SQL · transactions

Img ..> Api : packages

Prom ..> Api : scrape /metrics
Bbx ..> Api : probe /ready
Graf --> Prom

Api ..> ES : NDJSON logs\n(optional)

note bottom of Db
  Single service owns schema,
  Alembic migrations, transactional writes.
end note

@enduml
